{
  "stem": "4695.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But inside, it will be very luxury because I work by that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I will finish that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A matter of fact, our furniture the Germans took it out during the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they transport the furniture to Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But up to now, I don't know where this is.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- so-- And then comes-- exactly, I come home in September for '37.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in August '39 was the mobilization, the war, '39.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then the-- the war comes peace will be far away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I feel it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I feel the German propaganda.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I feel the Polish populations start taking over from the German the anti-Semitic ideas.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was afraid, because it is not-- in Germany, we have only 600,000 Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is a minimum.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But in Poland, 3.5 million population-- no, 35 million population-- we have 3-- no, Poland has-- wait a second.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yes, we have 3.5 million Jewish population, this is 10%.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But if we understand Poland, it's not 10% from the Polacks, because was beaten the 35 million was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So 5 million was raised White Russian, 7 million Ukrainians, and 3.5 million Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the Poland was only around 20 million.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, but still, we feel depressed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see then everything is going-- like they start to break up Jewish business, not to buy by Jew, then other thing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You start feeling-- it comes-- it is bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The situation is bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I could not describe how.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you feel that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was still working.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even I was-- when there was the mobilization, I was staying and working not far from where my wife was also working.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She comes in, crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You are staying here working.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's mobilization they call you to the army-- this-- two days before the war, or four days before the war.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
